All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractLoaderoService<T extends LoaderoModel>
    This abstract serves as a template for the service layer, that should be implemented for each Loadero model.
    FunctionBodyParser
    This class responsibility is to provide simple parser to parse TestUI code snippets from given path and return them as strings to later pass those snippets as part of JSON request.
    LoaderoClient
    Main entry point of the interaction with the Loadero API.
    LoaderoClientUtils
    This class provides some utility/helper functions for the package.
    LoaderoCrudController
    REST controller class responsible for CRUD actions related to Loadero tests.
    LoaderoGroup
    LoaderoGroup class is responsible for representing information retrieved from Loadero API /groups/groupId endpoint.
    LoaderoGroupService
    Implementation of AbstractLoaderoService that is responsible for CRUD operation related to LoaderoGroup object.
    LoaderoHttpClient
    Implementation of HttpClientBuilder for interacting with Loadero API.
    LoaderoModel
    Simple marker interface to mark Loadero related classes together.
    LoaderoModelFactory
    LoaderoModelFactory is a simple implementation of a Factory method pattern with intend to abstract creation of concrete LoaderoModels.
    LoaderoParticipant
    LoaderoParticipant class is responsible to represent information retrieved/updated from/to Loadero API /participants/participantId endpoint.
    LoaderoParticipantService
    Implementation of AbstractLoaderoService that is responsible for CRUD operation related to LoaderoParticipant object.
    LoaderoPollingService
    Implementation of AbstractLoaderoService that is responsible for polling operation.
    LoaderoRunInfo
    LoaderoRunInfo class is responsible for representing retrieved information during and after test runs.
    LoaderoScriptFileLoc
    LoaderoScriptFileLoc purpose is to store information about Loadero test script, that is used to run tests.
    LoaderoScriptFileService
    Implementation of AbstractLoaderoService that is responsible for CRUD operation related to LoaderoScriptFileLoc object.
    LoaderoServiceFactory
    Factory class that contains method that returns required service layer based on the provided LoaderoType.
    LoaderoTestOptions
    LoaderoTestDescription object is a configuration profile to specify test parameters for creation of Loadero tests.
    LoaderoTestOptionsService
    Implementation of AbstractLoaderoService that is responsible for CRUD operation related to LoaderoTestOptions object.
    LoaderoTestRunParticipantResult
    LoaderoTestRunParticipantResult represents the information about single participant test run result.
    LoaderoTestRunParticipantResultService
    Implementation of AbstractLoaderoService that is responsible for CRUD operation related to LoaderoTestRunParticipantResult object.
    LoaderoTestRunResult
    LoaderoTestRunResult class represents the information retrieved from Loadero /runs/:runID/results/.
    LoaderoTestRunResultService
    Implementation of AbstractLoaderoService that is responsible for CRUD operation related to LoaderoTestRunResult object.
    LoaderoType
    Enum types are used for creation/validation of concrete LoaderoModel classes.
    LoaderoUrlBuilder
    This class is responsible for building url endpoints for Loadero API.
